   "lat": null,
   "lng": null,
   "narrative": "Gerald D. McClellan was Holyoke High School, class of 1957, then the University of Massachusetts and St. John's University law. He was a first lieutenant in a United States Army armoured division in 1961. He came home to the law and was later appointed a probate judge. If you have further information about this veteran, please contact the City of Holyoke Veterans Graves Officer at (413) 322-5630 at 310 Appleton Street, 1st Floor, Holyoke, MA 01040.",
